### Export (ZIP + PDF)

#### [MODIFY] [src/pages/ReportView.tsx](file:///c:/Users/lilia/Escritorio/trip-companion-main%202/trip-companion-main/src/pages/ReportView.tsx)

**In [handleExport()](file:///c:/Users/lilia/Escritorio/trip-companion-main%202/trip-companion-main/src/pages/ReportView.tsx#372-566) and [handleExportZip()](file:///c:/Users/lilia/Escritorio/trip-companion-main%202/trip-companion-main/src/pages/ReportView.tsx#567-738) (PDF):**
If the user is Pro and has at least 2 odometer snapshots covering the report period, **add a summary card at the top of the first page** (above the trips table), using existing jsPDF draw calls:

```
┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
| ■ Resumen cuentakilómetros 2024                       |
| Inicio: 98.000 km (01/01/2024 · ITV)                 |
| Fin:   121.500 km (31/12/2024 · Taller)              |
| Km trabajo: 14.200 km  | Km privados: 9.300 km       |
| Uso laboral: 60,4%                                   |
└────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```
The card uses the same styling as the rest of the report (no extra page, no embedded photos in PDF).

**In [handleExportZip()](file:///c:/Users/lilia/Escritorio/trip-companion-main%202/trip-companion-main/src/pages/ReportView.tsx#567-738) (ZIP only):**
- Download the two odometer photos from Supabase Storage
- Add to ZIP as `odometro/foto_inicio_{date}.ext` and `odometro/foto_fin_{date}.ext`
- Same pattern as existing document downloads in [collectDocs()](file:///c:/Users/lilia/Escritorio/trip-companion-main%202/trip-companion-main/src/hooks/use-project-export.ts#52-133)

#### [MODIFY] [src/hooks/use-project-export.ts](file:///c:/Users/lilia/Escritorio/trip-companion-main%202/trip-companion-main/src/hooks/use-project-export.ts)
- No changes needed — photos are downloaded and added directly inside [handleExportZip](file:///c:/Users/lilia/Escritorio/trip-companion-main%202/trip-companion-main/src/pages/ReportView.tsx#567-738)

